* No = 3

---

## 🔹 Step 2: Entropy of whole dataset

Formula:
[
Entropy(S) = -p_1 \log_2 p_1 - p_2 \log_2 p_2
]

[
= -\frac{2}{5}\log_2\frac{2}{5} - \frac{3}{5}\log_2\frac{3}{5}
]

[
= -(0.4)(-1.32) - (0.6)(-0.736)
]

[
= 0.528 + 0.441 = 0.97 \ (approx)
]

👉 **Entropy(S) ≈ 0.97**

